{
  "stem": "14251.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And she knew Jews at a 100-meter distance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "All I know is any time I was around that woman, my mother told me I couldn't talk, not one word of anything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I was to be quiet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Well, the two children and I were playing in the sandbox.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I still remember the sandals that I had on that day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "In those times the sandals had a division or two in the soles.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So you had to be careful your feet didn't get pinched in as you walked.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] We were playing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I suddenly got up and said to her, well, I have to tell you something-- whispered-- and my mother said, it is rude to whisper.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "You know, here's more of that German discipline stuff.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I said, but I know I have to whisper this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I know this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "The woman finally felt sorry for me, I guess, and said to my mother, it's all right.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Let her whisper.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And I whispered to her, and I still remember it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "It was a sunny day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They sat under an umbrella.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I remember the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, can I-- while we're playing in the sandbox, can I just once say my name, Goldstein?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Thought she was going to fall out of her chair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she turned around and did what-- probably the only thing that she could think of-- and that was to say, don't you ever-- and with the finger to this day-- don't you ever say a word like that again.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, as if I had said some obscene word.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had to be quick-witted to handle these circumstances.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- but I was happy and went back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had said what I needed to say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the woman never caught on.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
